🔴 Module E — OPEN VOTING SYSTEM

👉 ANY address can vote on ANY proposal

mapping(bytes32 => mapping(address => bool)) public voted;
mapping(bytes32 => uint256) public yes;
mapping(bytes32 => uint256) public no;

function vote(bytes32 proposal, bool support) external {
    require(!voted[proposal][msg.sender]);

    voted[proposal][msg.sender] = true;

    if (support) yes[proposal]++;
    else no[proposal]++;
}



⚫ Module F — TEMPORAL OVERRIDE ENGINE

Latest consensus state wins:

mapping(bytes32 => bytes32) public activeState;
mapping(bytes32 => uint256) public timestamp;

function updateState(bytes32 entity, bytes32 newState) external {
    if (block.timestamp > timestamp[entity]) {
        activeState[entity] = newState;
        timestamp[entity] = block.timestamp;
    }
}



